{"tid":102963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"取代聚乙烯 蝦殼製作可分解購物袋！！！","createTime":"2017-02-01T03:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T14:18:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbe3899655b1737639135909e01fe47499133c0","tid":102963,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n農曆新年期間少不免會食蝦，寓意哈哈大笑和笑口常開。除非已經炸得酥脆，否則食蝦前剝殼非常合理，但蝦殼除了當作廚餘回收或垃圾丟掉，原來還有實際用途。有生物科技工程師研究了新的技術，以蝦殼作為原料製作購物袋，取代無法分解的聚乙烯塑膠袋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/115606_e44e02de69fc116f6bb8b93a28d0c549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F115606_e44e02de69fc116f6bb8b93a28d0c549.jpg&h=2ed9142a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國諾定咸大學和埃及尼羅大學的生物科技工程師團隊，發現只要利用蝦殼內的甲殼素，可以製成生物聚合物的納米複合材料。這材料不但可以取代無法在環境中分解的聚乙烯膠袋原料，而且成本亦非常便宜，更可以在自然界內自然分解。研究員以酸性物質浸泡甲殼素將碳酸鈣去除，再提煉出薄片狀的聚合物，經過處理後形成的薄膜就可以用作可分解的購物袋，減少對環境的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n來源：ettoday<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f75b4fbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁 <a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=61555aa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a> <br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=12c66358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\nThe post 取代聚乙烯 蝦殼製作可分解購物袋 appeared first on <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c60b61db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a> 玩生活‧樂科技."},{"pid":"fa0ab2b98863f18bffab2cdf1409aef5849e46b9","tid":102963,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1910160f4ac8def86a9ba3b532414262843390","tid":102963,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e816c900333550ded9b117b6c23550c002024a","tid":102963,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c15c3f9773a1a45f3ce99892de3a98cc33fa116","tid":102963,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:58:01.000Z","msg":"家陣有幾多公司用緊可自行分解膠袋"},{"pid":"38576382cf72907a9a64b18bc973666a626ed20d","tid":102963,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"難題係點樣回收先"},{"pid":"824756560a268aeb651fea9f9b620a6eb6f0814a","tid":102963,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"一千隻蝦殻做到幾多袋我唔知<br />\n<br />\n但肯定臭撚死"},{"pid":"6673f2236b9c114a9ce2ae3f2517375570ee6862","tid":102963,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cdb6e568c37b52fce68ea5a3d21585bdf1f9d5","tid":102963,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75918c1cee7242ec55a1203518ca121b46e44cf6","tid":102963,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaad9eaba18c5099545e58f4f52fe979